{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005740/extras/Untitleddesign1-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1727657217\" /><br><br>Board Wars ToT is a couch-op, local multiplayer board game intended for family/friend game nights. Players will take turns rolling dice to RUN across the board and Trick-Or-Treat. Instead of allowing the dice determine how many tiles you move, you as the player will have a certain amount of time to travel across the board to your desired tile. Land at a house to Trick-Or-Treat or land on a Special tile to switch up the score board. But be careful, as long as you have candy in your pockets, it can be stolen from other players and even other greedy monsters trying to catch your spoils. As a monster on Hallow's eve, you have only one goal, DELIVER THE MOST CANDY TO BIG BOSS !!!","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3005740?t=1727657217","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005740/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1727657217","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005740/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727657217","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005740/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1727657217","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h1>Developer's Notes</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>***Welcome all players. We want to first thank you for visiting our page. Our biggest goal is that you have an enjoyable experience while trick-or-treating. We want you to feel you struck a deal with this game! This game 